metadata.name: Wijayakusuma
metadata.description:
Wijayakusuma is the name of a flower that only blooms at night,  also called the night queen flower,
In Javanese mythology, whoever manages to own, plant, and see it bloom at night will have their hope come true.

Tells about the anxiety of seeing beauty along with the destruction of nature every day, hoping that everything that has been damaged will be beautiful again.
Inspired by the song wijayakusuma from Ardhito Pramono
